		<title>Things I have missed about summer in Ontario</title>
		<link>http://www.sowrey.org/2015/07/things-i-have-missed-about-summer-in-ontario/</link>
		<comments>http://www.sowrey.org/2015/07/things-i-have-missed-about-summer-in-ontario/#comments</comments>
		<pubDate>Fri, 31 Jul 2015 17:54:51 +0000</pubDate>
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Geoff]]></dc:creator>
